      "supportingFindings": [
        "Blood lead level 8.2 µg/dL is at or above the CDC reference value of 3.5 µg/dL.",
        "Microcytosis coexists with an elevated blood lead level; iron deficiency should also be evaluated."
      ],
      "cautions": [],
      "nextSteps": [
        "If the elevated result is capillary, obtain confirmatory venous testing on the CDC timeline.",
